cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.IR 

The paper focuses on the development of computer-based image analysis systems for the segmentation of glomeruli in renal histopathology using CNNs. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes two different CNN cascades for segmentation applications, which involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL). Finally, the paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with the analysis of whole slide images of the kidney.
